🔑 HDFS Write Mechanism Pipeline Setup pic: (/Users/hryhorii/Desktop/projects/win-won/src/main/resources/pictures/big_data/hadoop/Screenshot 2026-04-18 at 20.12.16.png) 🔑
   Example:
        - we do have new text file
        - client node ask  ~> name node:      i have a data to write
        - name node answer ~> client node:    here is ip's
        - client node ask  ~> data_node_1: i have data to write are you ready ?
                              data_node_1 ask ~> data_node 2: we do have data to write are you ready ?
                              data_node_2 ask ~> data_node 3: we do have data to write are you ready ?
                              data_node_3 answer ~> data_node 2: yes i am ready
                              data_node_2 answer ~> data_node 1: yes we are ready
                              data_node_1 answer ~> client node: yes we are ready
        - client node send file to data_node_1
                              data_node_1 send file to data_node_2
                              data_node_2 send file to data_node_3
        - acknowledge
            - data_node_3 send acknowledge (complete) to data_node_2
            - data_node_2 send acknowledge (complete) to data_node_1
            - data_node_1 send acknowledge to client node
            - client_node send acknowledge to name_node
            - name_node updated it's own meta_data









